        <item>
            <title>政府：有人用 AI 假冒特首李家超　伪造投资计划影片存心诈骗</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/01/10/cheater-used-chief-executive-face/tech-secure/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=cheater-used-chief-executive-face</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/01/10/cheater-used-chief-executive-face/tech-secure/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[蒋纳偲]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 09:59:08 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[资讯保安]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AI]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1214168</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>政府指，近日网上流传一条以人工智能伪造的影片，假冒香港特首李家超推介一响高回报的投资计划。政府严厉申斥不法之徒假冒特首并诱骗他人，并澄清有关影片全属伪造，存心诈骗。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1214279" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/download-1-144x144.jpeg" alt="" width="300" height="300" /></p><p>该影片疑似利用特首李家超出席活动后会见传媒的画面，配上人工智能生成的声音合成。片段中「李家超」呼吁市民投资一个应用程式，声称所获得的利润可以免税，帮助香港人应对全球通货膨胀等情况。</p><p>政府指，已转交警方跟进调查，并忠告市民切勿轻信类似的投资广告或推广影片。</p><p>这并不是李家超第一次成为诈骗广告的主角。前年他的头像被骗徒利用作为钓鱼网站的找来。</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20240109/s00001/1704795576871/%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%96%A5%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BAai%E8%A3%BD%E7%9F%AD%E7%89%87%E5%86%92%E6%9D%8E%E5%AE%B6%E8%B6%85%E5%AE%A3%E5%82%B3%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-%E5%B7%B2%E8%BD%89%E4%BA%A4%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5">明报</a><br /><b>相关文章:</b></p><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/28/gpt4all-no-need-internect-connection/tips-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">GPT4All 不需上网可用 AI【教学】离线安装 + 免 VPN 实试</a></li><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/07/meta-imagine/tips-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学】Meta 生成式 AI 绘图　多种画风选择 + 「手指」表现不俗</a></li><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/11/22/chatgpt-with-voice/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学】ChatGPT 语音对话，听得明广东话 + 直接语音回答</a></li></blockquote><p></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/10/cheater-used-chief-executive-face/tech-secure/">政府：有人用 AI 假冒特首李家超　伪造投资计划影片存心诈骗</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
