            <description>
                <![CDATA[<div class="html-div xe8uvvx xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1tlxs6b x1g8br2z x1gn5b1j x230xth x14ctfv x1okitfd x6ikm8r x10wlt62 x1y1aw1k xwib8y2 x1ye3gou xn6708d x1n2onr6 x1vjfegm x1mzt3pk x13faqbe" role="presentation"><div class="x9f619 x1n2onr6 x1ja2u2z __fb-light-mode" role="none"><div dir="auto">Sony 与 Honda 早在 2022 年 6 月已签署合资协议，正式成立 Sony Honda Mobility Inc，公司主要共同研发电动车，去年已发表第一辆纯电动车「AFEELA」。今日 Sony Honda 就于 CES 2024 上展示 AFEELA 实车，Sony Honda Mobility 更利用 Sony PS5 DualSense 手掣遥控 AFEELA 上台。</div></div></div><div dir="auto"></div><div dir="auto"></div><div dir="auto"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213868" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_092516-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_092516-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_092516-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></div><div dir="auto"></div><div dir="auto" style="text-align: center;">▲AFEELA 内笼可见軚盘设计新颖，科技感十足</div><div dir="auto"></div><div dir="auto">Sony Honda Mobility 是一间由 Sony 及 Honda 各占一半股份的合资公司，其合作设计的概念电动车 AFEELA 在 SEC 2023 已展出过，今年 SEC 2024 Sony Honda Mobility 社长川西泉在展示 AFEELA 实车时更利用 PlayStation 5 的 DualSense 遥控操控电车上台。</div><div dir="auto"></div><div class="html-div xe8uvvx xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1tlxs6b x1g8br2z x1gn5b1j x230xth x14ctfv x1okitfd x6ikm8r x10wlt62 x1y1aw1k xwib8y2 x1ye3gou xn6708d x1n2onr6 x1vjfegm x1mzt3pk x13faqbe" role="presentation"><div dir="auto"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213971" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_092955-1-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_092955-1-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_092955-1-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></div><div dir="auto"></div><div dir="auto" style="text-align: center;"><span style="text-align: center;">▲Sony Honda Mobility </span><span style="text-align: center;">社长</span><span style="text-align: center;">川西泉</span></div><div dir="auto"></div></div><div dir="auto"><div dir="auto"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213976" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_093156-1-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_093156-1-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_093156-1-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></div><div dir="auto"></div><div dir="auto" style="text-align: center;"><span style="text-align: center;">▲Sony Honda Mobility </span><span style="text-align: center;">社长</span><span style="text-align: center;">川西泉</span></div></div><div dir="auto"></div><div class="html-div xe8uvvx xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1tlxs6b x1g8br2z x1gn5b1j x230xth x14ctfv x1okitfd x6ikm8r x10wlt62 x1y1aw1k xwib8y2 x1ye3gou xn6708d x1n2onr6 x1vjfegm x1mzt3pk x13faqbe" role="presentation"><div dir="auto"></div><div dir="auto"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213977" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_093206_-1-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_093206_-1-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_093206_-1-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></div><div dir="auto"></div></div><div dir="auto"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213985" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/up